Program: Discovery
Title: Murder, Magic, and Medicine
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrw70
Last Broadcast Date: 09 May 1994
The history of extracting chemical substances from natural sources - including poisons: Breakthroughs in understanding the genetic basis of diseases such as muscular dystrophy: Distant galaxies are found to be moving - much to astronomers' surprise. Presented by Tracy Logan.